{
  "stem": "3928.2",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was selected for an officer's candidate school.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They took over what they call the Ludovica Academy.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Ludovica Academy used to be the-- like a West Point of Hungary, you know, in a small scale.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I was there in the-- you know, all kind of a training we had to go through.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "First of all, we all had to get split-naked and make sure, you know, you're not circumcised, so you're not Jewish.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "This was the first thing, you know?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That's the test you went through.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Second, you know, you have to go through a test that how you feel about the Third Reich, how you feel about the communism, how you feel about the Jews, would you follow order blindly if whatever order was given to you?",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So naturally, I mean, I had to sign everything, OK.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Because that's the reason I wanted to get in to get the information.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was there on a training.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And after I was trained, they put me into the headquarters, the division in Budapest.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The headquarters division in Budapest was in Andrassy Street.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That's a main street of Budapest.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And right across from the main-- where office was, was the Hungarian Nazi Party headquarters, on Andrassy ut 60.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That's what they-- what they called the Arrow Cross people, they were there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You know, I had very little to do with the Arrow Cross people, as such, because I was assigned as a liaison between the Hungarian army and the SS operations in Budapest and the surrounding area.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I had the first-hand information of everything, naturally.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was given full confidence, naturally.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "In fact, they even gave me the Panzer Cross, you know, I never even been in a Panzer, because they liked me so much, you know?",
      "word_count": 26
    }
  ],
